data.text:
Sahasam adventurous film directed by Yelleti Chandra Sekhar and Gopi Chand- Tapsi acted as hero heroines are running successfully with good quality talk wise. With Producer Prasad production values, Shyam dutt Photography, Sri Re-Recording, Art Director Rama Krishna, Editor Kotagiri high quality work Sahasam film got talk as successful film and collected around 6.53 Crores in first week. Area-wise

collection details are:

Nizam 2 Crores

Ceded 1.12,

Uttarandhra 78 Lakhs,

Guntur 60 Lakhs,

East Godavari 52 Lakhs,

Krishna 40 Lakhs,

West Godavari 39 Lakhs,

Nellore 29 Lakhs,

Overseas 43 Lakhs

Totally Sahasam film collected 6 Crores 53 Lakhs share and became a lucky film to Gopi Chand and Tapsi.
